>Native macOS design with SwiftUI\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Quick access via menu bar\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Keyboard shortcuts for fast interactions\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Dark mode support\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"coming-soon\">Coming Soon\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Mac App Store availability\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Additional AI model integrations\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>Custom themes and preferences\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>",{"headings":41,"localImagePaths":52,"remoteImagePaths":53,"frontmatter":54,"imagePaths":56},[42,46,50],{"depth":43,"slug":44,"text":45},1,"all-my-ai-100","All My AI 1.0.0",{"depth":47,"slug":48,"text":49},2,"new-features","New Features",{"depth":47,"slug":12,"text":51},"Coming Soon",[],[],{"app":7,"version":31,"date":55,"summary":33,"published":34},["Date","2025-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"],[],"zh-cn/all-my-ai-1.0.0",{"id":57,"data":59,"body":62,"filePath":63,"digest":64,"rendered":65},{"app":7,"version":31,"date":60,"summary":61,"published":34},["Date","2025-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"],"All My AI macOS 版首次公开发布","# All My AI 1.0.0\n\nAll My AI 正式版首次发布，为 macOS 带来统一的 AI 助手体验。\n\n## 新功能\n\n- 多 AI 模型统一界面\n- SwiftUI 原生 macOS 设计\n- 菜单栏快速访问\n- 快捷键支持高效交互\n- 深色模式支持\n\n## 即将推出\n\n- Mac App Store 上架\n- 更多 AI 模型集成\n- 自定义主题与偏好设置","src/content/changelog/zh-cn/all-my-ai-1.0.0.md","f29e519682fc8a80",{"html":66,"metadata":67},"\u003Ch1 id=\"all-my-ai-100\">All My AI 1.0.0\u003C/h1>\n\u003Cp>All My AI 正式版首次发布，为 macOS 带来统一的 AI 助手体验。\u003C/p>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"新功能\">新功能\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>多 AI 模型统一界面\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>SwiftUI 原生 macOS 设计\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>菜单栏快速访问\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>快捷键支持高效交互\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>深色模式支持\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>\n\u003Ch2 id=\"即将推出\">即将推出\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cul>\n\u003Cli>Mac App Store 上架\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>更多 AI 模型集成\u003C/li>\n\u003Cli>自定义主题与偏好设置\u003C/li>\n\u003C/ul>",{"headings":68,"localImagePaths":74,"remoteImagePaths":75,"frontmatter":76,"imagePaths":78},[69,70,72],{"depth":43,"slug":44,"text":45},{"depth":47,"slug":71,"text":71},"新功能